<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <!-- SEO -->
  <title>How to Convert Your Audience Into Paying Customers — Funnel Audit & Conversion System</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Stop losing followers who never buy. Audit your funnel, position your offer, and build a 5-email conversion sequence. AI-powered system for creators and digital product sellers." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="how to convert audience to customers, convert followers to buyers, creator funnel audit, offer positioning framework, email sequence for creators, digital product conversion" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://audience-to-customer-converter.vercel.app" />

  <!-- OG -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Audience-to-Customer Converter — Turn Followers Into Buyers" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Funnel audit, offer positioning framework, and 5-email conversion sequence builder. Three tools that fix the gap between audience and sales." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://audience-to-customer-converter.vercel.app/og-image.png" />

  <!-- Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
    "name": "Audience-to-Customer Converter",
    "applicationCategory": "BusinessApplication",
    "description": "AI-powered funnel audit, offer positioning framework, and email sequence builder for creators and digital product sellers.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "67.00", "priceCurrency": "USD" },
    "aggregateRating": { "@type": "AggregateRating", "ratingValue": "4.9", "reviewCount": "29" }
  }
  </script>

  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why does my audience not buy from me?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The most common reasons an audience doesn't convert to buyers are: no email list to bridge social followers to a sales environment, an unclear offer (people don't know exactly what they're buying), insufficient promotion frequency (most sales happen after the 5th touchpoint, not the 1st), a trust gap where content doesn't demonstrate that you can deliver the transformation you're selling, and pricing signals that feel misaligned with perceived value. The Audience-to-Customer Converter audits your specific setup and identifies which of these is your primary leak."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How do you convert social media followers into customers?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "The most reliable path from follower to customer has three steps: move them from social to email (where conversion rates are 10-20x higher than social), deliver consistent value that builds trust and demonstrates your expertise, then make offers that are specific, clearly positioned, and repeated regularly. Most creators fail at step one — they have no system to capture followers' email addresses before making an offer."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What is a good conversion rate for selling to an audience?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Conversion rates vary significantly by channel and audience temperature. Direct social-to-sale (cold) typically converts at 0.1–0.5%. Email sequences to warm subscribers convert at 1–3%. A dedicated sales page with traffic from warm sources converts at 2–5%. Repeat buyers convert at 20–40%. If your rates are below these benchmarks, the issue is usually trust, offer clarity, or promotion frequency — not audience size."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How many emails does it take to convert a follower into a buyer?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Research consistently shows that most sales happen between the 5th and 12th touchpoint. A cold follower who downloads a freebie and receives one sales email will convert at a fraction of the rate of someone who has received 5 emails that build trust before the offer is made. The 5-email sequence in the Audience-to-Customer Converter is structured to deliver value for the first four emails before making the direct offer in email five."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Caslon+Display:ital@0;1&family=Libre+Caslon+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Epilogue:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;1,300;1,400&family=Courier+Prime:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --cream: #F5EFE4;
      --cream2: #EDE5D6;
      --cream3: #E2D8C8;
      --burg: #6B1A2A;
      --burg2: #8B2A3E;
      --burg3: #C44A60;
      --burg-dim: #6B1A2A12;
      --ink: #1E1610;
      --ink2: #3A2E24;
      --ink3: #7A6E60;
      --ink4: #B0A490;
      --rule: #D4C8B4;
      --gold: #B88A20;
      --green: #1A6B3A;
      --white: #FFFDF8;
    }
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Epilogue', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif; }

    .container { max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 36px; }
    .wide { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 36px; }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      background: var(--burg);
      padding: 0 36px; height: 56px;
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif;
      font-size: 16px; font-style: italic; color: var(--cream);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--cream); color: var(--burg);
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 9px 20px; text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700; transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--cream2); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      background: var(--burg);
      padding: 80px 0 72px;
      border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-texture {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(180,80,100,0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(100,10,20,0.3) 0%, transparent 50%);
    }
    .hero-inner { position: relative; }
    .hero-kicker {
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #C48898; margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }
    .hero-kicker::before { content: ''; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: #C48898; opacity: 0.5; }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: clamp(44px, 7vw, 88px);
      font-weight: 400; font-style: italic;
      color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.0;
      margin-bottom: 28px; letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .hero-h1 strong { font-style: normal; font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 16px; color: #C48898;
      max-width: 520px; line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 44px; font-weight: 300;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 16px 40px; text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700; transition: all 0.2s; display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #C89A30; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(184,138,32,0.3); }
    .btn-ghost {
      color: #8A5A68; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #4A2A38; padding-bottom: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase; transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--cream); border-color: #8A5A68; }
    .hero-stats {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); max-width: 560px;
    }
    .stat-box {
      padding: 18px 16px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-box:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif;
      font-size: 30px; font-style: italic; color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8A5A68;
    }

    /* SECTIONS */
    .section { padding: 88px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .eyebrow {
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ink4); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 60px); font-style: italic;
      line-height: 1.0; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .section-title strong { font-style: normal; font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--burg); }
    .section-sub {
      font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink3); max-width: 520px;
      line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 52px;
    }

    /* TRUTH SECTION */
    .truth-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--rule); border: 1px solid var(--rule); margin-top: 48px; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) { .truth-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .truth-item { background: var(--white); padding: 28px 30px; }
    .truth-num {
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif;
      font-size: 48px; font-style: italic; color: var(--rule);
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .truth-text { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink3); font-style: italic; line-height: 1.7; }
    .truth-text strong { font-style: normal; color: var(--burg); font-weight: 700; }

    /* TOOLS */
    .tool-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .tool-item {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr;
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    .tool-num {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: var(--burg); color: var(--gold);
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif;
      font-size: 28px; font-style: italic;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--burg2);
    }
    .tool-body { padding: 24px 28px; }
    .tool-tag {
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
      font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--burg); margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .tool-name {
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif;
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .tool-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink3); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 300; }
    .tool-features { display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .tool-feat {
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 4px 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--rule); color: var(--ink4); text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    /* FUNNEL LEAKS */
    .leaks-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule); margin-top: 48px; max-width: 640px; }
    .leak-row {
      display: flex; gap: 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }
    .leak-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .leak-num {
      min-width: 56px; padding: 20px 16px;
      background: var(--burg); color: var(--gold);
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif;
      font-size: 22px; font-style: italic;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--burg2); flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .leak-body { padding: 18px 22px; background: var(--white); }
    .leak-title {
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif;
      font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .leak-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink3); line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 300; }

    /* TESTIMONIALS */
    .test-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-top: 48px; }
    .test-card {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 28px; border-top: 3px solid var(--burg);
    }
    .stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .test-card p { font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 300; }
    .test-attr { font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--ink4); text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* PRICING */
    .pricing-card {
      max-width: 520px; margin: 48px auto 0;
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      border-top: 4px solid var(--burg); overflow: hidden;
    }
    .pricing-top { background: var(--burg); padding: 40px 44px; text-align: center; }
    .pricing-kicker { font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #C48898; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .price { font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif; font-size: 80px; font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); line-height: 1; }
    .price-sub { font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8A5A68; margin-top: 8px; }
    .pricing-body { padding: 36px 44px; }
    .feature-list { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .feature-list li { display: flex; gap: 12px; padding: 11px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.5; }
    .feature-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .check { color: var(--burg); flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 2px; }
    .btn-purchase {
      display: block; width: 100%;
      background: var(--burg); color: var(--cream);
      font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 18px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700; transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-purchase:hover { background: var(--burg2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .guarantee { text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--ink4); text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { margin-top: 48px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--white); }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
    .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .faq-q {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 16px; padding: 22px 28px; cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif;
      font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.3;
      background: none; border: none; width: 100%; text-align: left; transition: background 0.15s;
    }
    .faq-q:hover { background: var(--cream2); }
    .faq-toggle { color: var(--burg); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: sans-serif; }
    .faq-a { display: none; padding: 0 28px 22px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink3); line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { background: var(--burg); padding: 100px 0; border-top: 4px solid var(--gold); text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(36px, 6vw, 72px); font-style: italic; font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream); line-height: 1.0; margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .cta-section h2 strong { font-style: normal; font-family: 'Libre Caslon Text', serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold); }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 15px; color: #C48898; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 420px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; line-height: 1.8; font-weight: 300; }
    .cta-note { margin-top: 16px; font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: #8A5A68; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer { padding: 28px 36px; border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; background: var(--cream2); }
    .footer-logo { font-family: 'Libre Caslon Display', serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: italic; color: var(--ink3); }
    .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; }
    .footer-links a { font-family: 'Courier Prime', monospace; font-size: 9px; color: var(--ink4); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    /* ANIMATIONS */
    @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px); } to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); } }
    .hero-inner > * { animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both; opacity: 0; }
    .hero-kicker  { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
    .hero-h1      { animation-delay: 0.12s; }
    .hero-sub     { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .hero-actions { animation-delay: 0.26s; }
    .hero-stats   { animation-delay: 0.32s; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container, .wide { padding: 0 20px; }
      .section { padding: 60px 0; }
      nav { padding: 0 20px; }
      .pricing-top, .pricing-body { padding: 28px 24px; }
      footer { padding: 20px; }
      .hero-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Audience-to-Customer Converter</a>
  <a href="https://malikreagan.gumroad.com/l/audience-to-customer-converter" class="nav-cta">Get It — $67</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-texture"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-kicker">Audience-to-Customer Converter</div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1">
        Your audience likes you.<br/>
        They just won't<br/>
        <strong>buy from you.</strong>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        That's not an audience problem. It's a system problem. The Audience-to-Customer Converter gives you the three tools that fix it.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://malikreagan.gumroad.com/l/audience-to-customer-converter" class="btn-primary">Get the Converter — $67</a>
        <a href="#tools" class="btn-ghost">See all three tools ↓</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">3</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Tools inside</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">5</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Funnel leaks identified</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">6</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Offer frameworks</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
          <div class="stat-num">5</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Email sequence</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">The real problem</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">It's not your content.<br/>It's your <strong>system.</strong></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Most creators with conversion problems aren't bad at marketing. They're missing one or more of the same five things.</p>
    <div class="truth-grid">
      <div class="truth-item">
        <div class="truth-num">01</div>
        <p class="truth-text">Your audience lives on social but your offer lives somewhere else. There's <strong>no bridge between them.</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-item">
        <div class="truth-num">02</div>
        <p class="truth-text">Your offer isn't clear enough. "What exactly am I buying?" is a question that <strong>always beats purchase.</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-item">
        <div class="truth-num">03</div>
        <p class="truth-text">You promoted once at launch and never again. <strong>Most sales happen after the 5th mention,</strong> not the first.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-item">
        <div class="truth-num">04</div>
        <p class="truth-text">Your content is good but it doesn't <strong>prove you can deliver</strong> the transformation you're selling.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- TOOLS -->
<section class="section" id="tools">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">What's inside</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three tools.<br/>One <strong>conversion system.</strong></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Each tool fixes a different part of the gap between audience and sales.</p>
    <div class="tool-list">
      <div class="tool-item">
        <div class="tool-num">01</div>
        <div class="tool-body">
          <div class="tool-tag">Diagnosis</div>
          <div class="tool-name">AI Funnel Audit</div>
          <div class="tool-desc">Answer 8 questions about your audience, platform, email list, offer, promotion habits, and sales page. The AI audits your specific setup and returns a conversion health score, your single biggest leak, and a prioritised fix list with time-to-implement for each action.</div>
          <div class="tool-features">
            <span class="tool-feat">Conversion health score</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">Top leak identified</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">5 ranked fixes</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">Impact estimates</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-item">
        <div class="tool-num">02</div>
        <div class="tool-body">
          <div class="tool-tag">Positioning</div>
          <div class="tool-name">Offer Positioning Framework</div>
          <div class="tool-desc">Six frameworks for writing offer copy that converts followers into buyers. Fill in the fields for each framework — the positioning statement updates live as you type. Covers outcome statements, ROI framing, objection killing, social proof, cost of inaction, and specificity hooks.</div>
          <div class="tool-features">
            <span class="tool-feat">6 frameworks</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">Live preview</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">One-click copy</span>
            <span class="tool-feat">Works for any offer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tool-item">
        <div class="tool-num">03</div>
        <div class="tool-body">
          <div class="tool-tag">Conversion</div>
          <div class="tool-name">5-Email Sequence Builder</div>
