        <div class="leak-num">4</div>
        <div class="leak-body">
          <div class="leak-title">Wrong Price Signal</div>
          <div class="leak-desc">Price too low signals low value. Price too high without sufficient trust signals risk. Both kill conversion — for opposite reasons.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="leak-row">
        <div class="leak-num">5</div>
        <div class="leak-body">
          <div class="leak-title">Invisible Offer</div>
          <div class="leak-desc">You promote once at launch and go quiet. Most sales happen between the 5th and 12th touchpoint. Silence after launch is revenue left behind.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

